post0.content: A Test Post . I want to own my blog this time… but I really don’t want to spin up a server and set up Wordpress or whatever. So, I am trying fastpages - we’ll see how it goes! .

page1.title: About
page1.content: I am very interested in some cognitive science ideas, and I feel like I have a unique perspective to add as a Machine Learning / NLP practitioner. Specifically, I am thinking a lot about: . Predictive Processing | #SobSquad and Douglas Tatryn’s BioEmotive Framework | Van der Kolk / The Body Keeps the Score | Schmidhuber’s Mind Body Program | Valery Krupnik’s research | .
